RACE.RACE_TEXT: RILLITO RACE 4 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 67. Maiden Special Weight Purse 8500. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND OLDER. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MANY AMBITIONS Dueled three wide early stages, advanced with adjoining outside rival at three-eighths pole, match raced inside of rival until briefly losing the lead at the three-sixteenths pole, battled back along the rail to regain the lead at the sixteenth pole, resolutely held off one final bid from nagging rival in closing stages. ANGRY EMMY Stalked four wide into the first turn, commenced at the seven-sixteenths pole, joined inner rival at half mile pole, match raced outside to the three-sixteenths where runner gained brief lead, overtaken at the sixteenth pole, made one final bid, just missed. OJO FELIZ Vied for lead between rivals early, took out of spot at seven-sixteenths pole, asked from that point, never challenged top two. WITCHES DANCE Taken ahold of first turn, two path, moved at five-sixteenths pole, not enough to have a say in result. GEBO Held rail and lead into the first turn, dueled with two outside rivals up to the three-eighths pole where he was overtaken, never a match. DUKE CITY KITTY Taken back along the rail, asked at the three-eighths pole, never fired.

ENTRY.COMMENT: Taken back along rail, asked 3/8, never fired

ENTRY.COMMENT: Taken ahold of, 2w first, moved 5/16ths, not enough
